  <script>
    const CONFIG = {
      titulo: 'Chá Rifa da Luara',
      sorteioISO: '2025-10-26T20:00:00-03:00',
      whats: '5511984891131',
      mensagemZap: 'Quero participar do Chá Rifa da Luara! Meu número é __NUM__.',
      adminPIN: '369741',
      storageKey: 'rifa_luara_v3'
    };

    const linkZapBase = `https://wa.me/${CONFIG.whats}`;
    const btnWhats = document.getElementById('btnWhats');
    const linkWhats = document.getElementById('linkWhats');
    if(btnWhats) btnWhats.href = linkZapBase + '?text=' + encodeURIComponent('Olá! Quero participar do Chá Rifa da Luara.');
    if(linkWhats) linkWhats.href = btnWhats.href;

    document.getElementById('btnAgenda').addEventListener('click',()=>{
      const start = new Date(CONFIG.sorteioISO);
      const end   = new Date(start.getTime()+60*60*1000);
      const fmt = (d)=>d.toISOString().replaceAll('-','').replaceAll(':','').replace('.000','');
      const url = new URL('https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render');
      url.searchParams.set('action','TEMPLATE');
      url.searchParams.set('text', CONFIG.titulo + ' — Sorteio');
      url.searchParams.set('dates', `${fmt(start)}/${fmt(end)}`);
      url.searchParams.set('details','Sorteio pela Loteria Federal às 20:00.');
      window.open(url.toString(),'_blank');
    });

    const LS = { load(){ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(CONFIG.storageKey)||'{}'); }catch(e){return {}} }, save(s){ localStorage.setItem(CONFIG.storageKey, JSON.stringify(s)); } };
    let state = LS.load();

    const range = (n)=> n<=20?'P': (n<=60?'M': (n<=100?'G':'GG'));

    function render(){
      const grid=document.getElementById('grid'); grid.innerHTML='';
      let liv=0,res=0,ocu=0,ent=0;
      for(let n=1;n<=150;n++){ const s=state[n]||{status:'free'}; const a=document.createElement('button');
        const cls=(s.status==='busy'||s.status==='reserved'||s.status==='gifted')?s.status:'';
        a.className='num '+cls; a.textContent=n.toString().padStart(2,'0'); a.dataset.n=n; a.dataset.range=range(n);
        a.title=(s.status==='free'?'Livre':(s.status==='busy'?'Ocupado':(s.status==='gifted'?'Entregue':'Reservado')))+(s.nome?` — ${s.nome}`:'');
        a.addEventListener('click',()=>onClickNumber(n)); grid.appendChild(a);
        if(s.status==='free') liv++; else if(s.status==='reserved') res++; else if(s.status==='busy') ocu++; else if(s.status==='gifted') ent++; }
      const r=document.getElementById('resume'); if(r) r.textContent=`Livres: ${liv} • Reservados: ${res} • Ocupados: ${ocu} • Entregues: ${ent}`; }

    function onClickNumber(n){ const s=state[n]||{status:'free'};
      if(!ADMIN.enabled){ if(s.status==='busy' || s.status==='gifted'){ alert('Este número não está disponível.'); return; } openReserva(n); return; }
      openManage(n);
    }

    const dlg=document.getElementById('dlg'); const dlgNum=document.getElementById('dlgNum');
    const dlgFaixa=document.getElementById('dlgFaixa'); const inpNome=document.getElementById('inpNome');
    const inpTel=document.getElementById('inpTel'); const btnZapReserva=document.getElementById('btnZapReserva');

    function openReserva(n){ dlgNum.textContent=n.toString().padStart(2,'0'); dlgFaixa.textContent=range(n);
      const s=state[n]||{status:'free'}; inpNome.value=s.nome||''; inpTel.value=s.tel||'';
      const msg=CONFIG.mensagemZap.replace('__NUM__',n); btnZapReserva.href=linkZapBase+'?text='+encodeURIComponent(msg);
      dlg.showModal(); inpNome.focus(); document.getElementById('btnConfirm').onclick=()=>{ state[n]={status:'reserved',nome:inpNome.value.trim(),tel:inpTel.value.trim(),at:Date.now()}; LS.save(state); render(); dlg.close(); };
      document.getElementById('btnCancel').onclick=()=>dlg.close(); }

    const ADMIN={enabled:false}; const dlgAdmin=document.getElementById('dlgAdmin');
    document.getElementById('fabAdmin').onclick=()=> dlgAdmin.showModal();
    document.getElementById('btnPinCancel').onclick=()=> dlgAdmin.close();
    document.getElementById('btnPinOk').onclick=()=>{ const pin=document.getElementById('inpPin').value.trim();
      if(pin === CONFIG.adminPIN){ ADMIN.enabled=true; document.body.classList.add('admin'); alert('Modo anfitrião ativado! Toque em um número.'); dlgAdmin.close(); }
      else alert('PIN incorreto.'); };

    function openManage(n){ const dlgM=document.getElementById('dlgManage'); const mNum=document.getElementById('mNum'); const mNome=document.getElementById('mNome'); const mTel=document.getElementById('mTel');
      const s=state[n]||{status:'free'}; mNum.textContent=n.toString().padStart(2,'0'); mNome.value=s.nome||''; mTel.value=s.tel||'';
      function save(status){ state[n]={status,nome:mNome.value.trim(),tel:mTel.value.trim(),at:Date.now()}; LS.save(state); render(); dlgM.close(); }
      document.getElementById('mLivre').onclick=()=> save('free');
      document.getElementById('mReservar').onclick=()=> save('reserved');
      document.getElementById('mOcupar').onclick=()=> save('busy');
      document.getElementById('mEntregue').onclick=()=> save('gifted');
      document.getElementById('mFechar').onclick=()=> dlgM.close();
      dlgM.showModal(); }

    // Sobe o botão se detectar banner do tiiny; aceita override via ?fab=top ou ?fab=160
    (function fixFabForHosts(){
      const isTiiny = /tiiny(\.host|\.site)/i.test(location.hostname) || /tiiny/i.test(location.href);
      const extra = isTiiny ? 140 : 18; // ajuste se necessário
      document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--fab-offset', extra + 'px');
      const q = new URLSearchParams(location.search).get('fab');
      if(q === 'top'){ document.getElementById('fabAdmin')?.classList.add('top'); }
      else if(q && /^\d+$/.test(q)){ document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--fab-offset', q + 'px'); }
    })();

    window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', ()=>{
      setTimeout(()=>{
        const ok = document.getElementById('grid')?.children.length > 0;
        if(!ok){
          const b = document.createElement('div');
          b.className = 'compat-banner';
          b.innerHTML = 'Para ver os números, abra no navegador (Chrome/Safari). O visualizador do app bloqueia scripts. '+
                        '<strong>Android:</strong> três pontinhos → “Abrir com… Chrome”. '+
                        '<strong>iPhone:</strong> Salvar em Arquivos → abrir no Safari.';
          document.body.prepend(b);
          try{ alert('Abra no navegador para ver e escolher os números.'); }catch(e){}
        }
      }, 1200);
    });

    render();
  </script>
